{"tid":2285832,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"上班尖峰！馬尾妹「脖子纏蛇」地鐵坐6站　他直擊嚇壞：蛇對人吐信","createTime":"2020-11-14T12:38:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T18:05:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f47512fbfc570c19a44454d9d8fb1e4bca86c8a","tid":2285832,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-14T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5268/d5268212.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5268%2Fd5268212.jpg&h=0fb8f361&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一名網友今上午7點多搭乘北捷時，驚見有位女生不僅帶了兩個寵物箱，更將較大條的蛇<br />\n纏繞在脖子上，雖然後方乘客似乎沒察覺，但這明顯違反規定，畫面也讓人不寒而慄。<br />\n<br />\n目擊的H先生向《ETtoday新聞雲》記者表示，當時該名女乘客在三重站附近上車，隨身帶<br />\n了一個行李箱及兩個寵物箱，箱內放有一條小蛇，但比較大條的直接纏繞在脖子上，最後<br />\n一直搭到行天宮站才下車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201113/1853769.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20201113%2F1853769.htm&d=4dTSSGngnNsQf06YPjcNyxjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=e3ea65ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20201113/1853769.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4c3473fdcd2a53f518517cce044a4b0db536a00c","tid":2285832,"uid":379710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T18:05:32.000Z","msg":"球蠎都驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}